Name: advanced sleep phase syndrome 1
Definition: An advanced sleep phase syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the PER2 gene on chromosome 2q37.

Name: advanced sleep phase syndrome 2
Definition: An advanced sleep phase syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the CSNK1D gene on chromosome 17q25.

Name: advanced sleep phase syndrome 3
Definition: An advanced sleep phase syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the PER3 gene on chromosome 1p36.23.
